      "content": "but apophenia feels like such a dismissive way to put it when it's happening this much. it's not just random... like, yesterday i saw 44 and then literally 5 minutes later a news headline mentioned something about the \"44th\" something. \n\nand then there's the names. i keep seeing names like \"Leo\" or \"Iris\" right after these numbers. it feels way more intentional than just my brain playing tricks on me. don't you think it's possible there's a layer of meaning that isn't just math? like a frequency or something?",
